snippet.title: NiftyVille Teaser - New Open World NFT MMO Game - Play To Earn - Built On Ethereum
snippet.description:
NiftyVille is the new flagship play to earn Ethereum Blockchain NFT game, built by Onessus, the creators of the hit NFT game, HodlGod. Earn NFTs, socialize, collect, start a business, own real estate, and more in this upcoming game based on the real world.

Who will you be in NiftyVille?

For more info visit: https://NiftyVille.net
Follow us to stay up to date! https://twitter.com/NiftyVille
